node.text: @ryanchef87 love dumplings 🥟

“Words can’t express my fillings for you” 🥰⁠
.⁠
Dumplings, for me, is one of those food I can have for breakfast, lunch, dinner or even snack. YES, literally all day every day. 🥟⁠
.⁠
Killed two birds with one stone; so I mastered a new wrapping method (credit to @nom_life )as well as this amazingly crispy layer (credits to @sohlae ).💯⁠
.
